data.description: Spacious remodeled four bedroom rambler situated in a great residential neighborhood. Upon arrival you will be delighted with an abundance of natural light in the large living room. The eat-in kitchen is a chefs delight with granite counters & newer cabinets. Huge lower level which could be a great in-law suite, featuring; a bedroom and a large family room. The backyard is a gardener's paradise with plenty of space to garden and it's also the perfect place to entertain. The home is complete with an oversized two car garage with a large driveway for additional off-street parking. Located in a convenient area close to freeway access, downtown and shopping. Don't miss your opportunity to own this charming home in a great Brooklyn Center neighborhood!
